== Configure Apple's DVD Player not to autoplay DVDs.<br>  ==

<br>Get to Mac OS X global system preferences. 

Open up the "CDs &amp; DVDs" section in the "Hardware" category, add VLC to the list of apps next to "When you insert a video DVD" and select it afterwards. That's it. 

<br> 

Note that setting up VLC for Audio CD playback is possible this way as well. <br> 

